Command Editor.read executed: file_path='/Users/user1/CODE/Tester/MetaGPT-2/humaneval_baseline-4/int_to_mini_roman.py' block_content='001|def int_to_mini_roman(number):\n002|    values = [1000, 900, 500, 400, 100, 90, 50, 40, 10, 9, 5, 4, 1]\n003|    numerals = ["M", "CM", "D", "CD", "C", "XC", "L", "XL", "X", "IX", "V", "IV", "I"]\n004|    result = []\n005|    i = 0\n006|    while number > 0:\n007|        count = number // values[i]\n008|        if count:\n009|            result.append(numerals[i] * count)\n010|            number -= values[i] * count\n011|        i += 1\n012|    return "".join(result).lower()'

